50|$|Buttock {{cells are}} cells having a notched {{appearance}} {{that are found}} in certain malignancies, such as non-Hodgkin's lymphoma (including follicular lymphoma), Alibert-Bazin syndrome, and <b>Sézary</b> <b>syndrome.</b>|$|E
